{"tid":1369192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴打們727 728和之後可以做的事 文宣組請入","createTime":"2019-07-26T15:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T18:37:45.000Z","uid":251152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea03d0d8a9b257acbf022c364da84650dae2d4d5","tid":1369192,"uid":251152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:46:11.000Z","msg":"巴打們,我整理左少許意見方法,會長篇一D,但可以就睇/聽哂<br />\n因為林奠721打步棋太錯,其實今後我地保守行動盲會WIN<br />\n我地首要目標係呢個:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uWYPMC6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWYPMC6.png&h=24830456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為721元朗事件最應該負責既始作俑者係佢<br />\n犬方一哥係紙板人，鄧狗就係元黑鷹派，如果要做直指鄧狗等佢下界無得上傷害會大d。<br />\n而李奠冇左狗既支持係如同打斷雙腳<br />\n<br />\n【熟悉新界鄉事外嫁女烽煙爆警隊二哥不為人知身世，透露元朗襲擊引起真正原居民不滿】<br />\n熟悉新界鄉事外嫁女王太（音）烽煙《風波裏的茶杯》，爆警隊二哥不為人知身世，透露元朗襲擊引起真正原居民不滿，因為已對當區樓市帶來影響，擔心7&bull;27若再發生大衝突，會令樓價大跌影響原居民利益。王太並拆解了元朗恐襲事件與鄉事派系之爭、與鄧炳強何君堯等人的關係，在訪問中敬告各位叔父727不要搞遊行人士，「唔好以為二哥會保護到你哋」！<br />\n<br />\n*補充資料：王太（音）mic後向《風波裏的茶杯》解釋，鄧炳強家族並非清朝前已在新界生活的原居民，而是後來才到新界生活的，準確來說新界人稱他為「圍頭仔」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/287013041410957/posts/2297782073667367?s=1456821140&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F287013041410957%2Fposts%2F2297782073667367%3Fs%3D1456821140%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwUyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=350982ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/287013041410957/posts/2297782073667367?s=1456821140&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"9ddb08d64626c82d9460441cf231e7642a494b55","tid":1369192,"uid":251152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:48:23.000Z","msg":"劉細良同蕭若元的分析都很好, 老蕭直情將21/7個局好似寫劇本一樣勾劃整個故事, 環環緊扣, 由事前20/7動員到西環設局元朗圍剿, 有如瀝瀝在目. 有時間要睇睇<br />\n蕭若元<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/memehkdotcom/videos/390227945185414/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmemehkdotcom%2Fvideos%2F390227945185414%2F&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwUyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=c978cf06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/memehkdotcom/videos/390227945185414/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/memehkdotcom/videos/374833159885648/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmemehkdotcom%2Fvideos%2F374833159885648%2F&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwUyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=eb0326e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/memehkdotcom/videos/374833159885648/</a><br />\n劉細良 , 佢有講到運動過後的事,係長D,但係巴打可以就聽哂<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=TfE4DnfVj-Q&amp;fbclid=IwAR35TU28t4Y1IP-_Rx84J2_Y21qnatxH3e-NXSNd-Hnk9lN8q5RgsVg2ZUY&amp;app=desktop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3DTfE4DnfVj-Q%26fbclid%3DIwAR35TU28t4Y1IP-_Rx84J2_Y21qnatxH3e-NXSNd-Hnk9lN8q5RgsVg2ZUY%26app%3Ddesktop&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwUyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=ced3b4ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=TfE4DnfVj-Q&amp;fbclid=IwAR35TU28t4Y1IP-_Rx84J2_Y21qnatxH3e-NXSNd-Hnk9lN8q5RgsVg2ZUY&amp;app=desktop</a>"},{"pid":"cfeba3f63efb93bf7680945be99d938aca4c6406","tid":1369192,"uid":251152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:48:44.000Z","msg":"發夢見到一個情況:犬方一哥係紙板人，鄧狗就係元黑鷹派，如果要做直指鄧狗等佢下界無得上傷害會大d。要玩細狗玩到崩潰有個方法，圍狗屋大玩行為藝術不衝擊，例如將狗屋化做連朧屋，唱歌聖詩標銅玩齊，但一出黎清就不守即散，等d狗上哂裝備十個鐘齋企無得打無得發洩，佢地谷住谷住一兩次實癲。而家無事係每次d狗一出黎就可以亂咁咬人，又可以隨意屙尿射人個頭無責任，平時犬隻集訓都唔咁射頭啦，未俾同類屌過咩。"},{"pid":"068ebcf18bf394a20318c6b66eac224e4ba2bb6a","tid":1369192,"uid":251152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"最後<br />\n曙光初現, 記得唔好衝動, 比位政府翻新和重新抱團, 唔好沖擊新界鄉村, 唔好觸動一國底線, 唔好俾藉口出動解放軍.<br />\n<br />\n兄弟們<br />\n727見<br />\n香港加油!"},{"pid":"d72aa88c603230290816608ce29dff7da711a2aa","tid":1369192,"uid":50809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"068ebcf18bf394a20318c6b66eac224e4ba2bb